Hook: "Person wey no get helper supposed to get sense."

Body: This phrase has guided me throughout this journey. In corporate America, you are often your own best helper.

CRABuddy is the "sense" I’ve built to help me—and you—navigate the complexities of clinical research. It’s the intelligence layer that ensures your achievements are logged, your logistics are stored, and your career is audit-ready.

